096-116a @#/ /dug zhi bar byed pa zhes bya ba/ bdud rtsi sman gyi lha mo nor gyi rgyun la phyag 'tshal lo/ /tad+ya thA/ oM su ru su ru ka/ ba ra ba ra ke/ bi ri hi ri/ shud d+he bi shud d+he swA hA/ sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi bden pa dang / gzi brjid kyis klu'i dug dang / sbrul gyi dug dang / sbyar ba'i dug dang / brlangs kyi dug dang / rtsa ba'i dug dang / gcan gzanamache ba'i dug bcom mo/ /dug nges par bcom mo zhes brjod par bya'o/ /dug thams cad zhi bar byed pa'i gzungs rdzogs so//
